Rewrapped - Season 2, Episode 3




Let Them Eat Koffee Kake!

It's a competition packed with fresh baked ideas! In the Recreate Round, one chef runs into a sticky situation with his Koffee Kake. Then in the Innovate Round, one chef tries to rise above the competition by using Wagyu Steak with a Koffee Kake Beurre Blanc. Can this dish butter up the judges? Get ready for a delicious, cinnamon-sprinkled episode of Rewrapped!




Original Air Date: 22-Sep-2014
